--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.4.2 (2018-12-07)
I: Remove email information from message

* Version 0.4.1 (2018-11-27)
I: Minor style improvements

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-10-29)
F: Add option to disable MariaDB backups (mariadb_run_backup_state)

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-09-14)
I: Add 'no_log' parameter to sensitive tasks

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-08-08)
F: Add options to configure 'databases' and 'users'

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-08-07)
F: Add tasks to run initial MySQL installation (mysql_secure_installation)

* Version 0.1.3 (2018-07-19)
I: Minor configuration file improvement

* Version 0.1.2 (2018-07-19)
I: Change the default 'file_mode_mariadb_backup_file' permissions

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-07-19)
I: Change the default 'mariadb_run_backup_hour'

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-07-19)
F: Initial release
